          "description": "Declares GDScriptByteCodeGenerator, which translates the AST/IR into the integer opcode stream stored in GDScriptFunction. Emits all OPCODE_* values and populates the typed dispatch-table vectors.",
          "key_classes": ["GDScriptByteCodeGenerator"]
